data.description: Do not miss the opportunity to own this private, beautiful no HAO estate property in excellent condition with a pond view and professionally landscaped, very open and light. Smoke free, pet free. Three bedrooms on main floor plus one bedroom beside of a large bonus room with vaulted ceiling. Hardwood floors in the main floor: kitchen, dining room, laundry. Large kitchen with island and breakfast area opens to family and dining rooms. Fireplace, garage and nice back deck.
